data.description: Beautifully remodeled 1 story home, 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, open concept with a Flex room. Custom made 2 tone kitchen cabinets with Butcher Block Countertops and luxury Vinyl flooring throughout. Everything has been updated , Refrigerated A/C, Ductwork, Electrical, Plumbing, Roof, Water Heater, Windows and Garage conversion Plus Custom blinds. Located in a Stablished neighborhood, walking distance to Andres High and easy access to 54 and Loop 375 surrounded by new restaurants and shopping!! Come by today!!
